                                            Highest Cancer Death
                   Business questiom
Which countries have the highest possible cancer deaths? 

          Query
SELECT
  country_name,
  MAX(possible_cancer_deaths) AS highest_death
FROM cancer_data
GROUP BY country_name
ORDER BY highest_death DESC;

           Insight
This shows the country with the highest number of death cases,which means in those high death country there are still people that are at risks.

     Recommendation
We should focus on early test, detection and awareness of cancer in these countries.
